    "16604607234acd9044": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "1c50e393-e4fc-41cc-8d7a-88a2d8d03645": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Tip #1 MAKE A RENDEZVOUS POINT",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "8720fd58-205b-4bf5-b987-252ac7701d2a": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Festivals are crazy busy. <\/p><p>Navigating the crowds is challenging enough, but add a few drinks into the mix and your sense of direction is sure to be thrown off balance, making it super easy to get lost. <\/p><p>Decide on a meeting place with your friends, somewhere that’s easy for the whole group to remember. Maybe back at your tent, or next to your favorite food stall. And if someone heads off for a toilet break or to grab a bite, make sure that the whole group waits in one place until they’re back.<\/p>",
            "description_padding": 32
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "1c50e393-e4fc-41cc-8d7a-88a2d8d03645",
