    "16581501774a32acf8": {
      "type": "loop-article-img-txt",
      "blocks": {
        "15d54bfe-1b48-43c0-9fad-0527a7874216": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "TIP #2 BRING WET WIPES AND SANITIZER WITH YOU",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "16581501770ad7ecad-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>There’s no denying it: Festivals are grimy. <\/p><p>We’re talking mounds of mud, sweaty bodies and “the dreaded toilets” sort of grimy. <\/p><p>Showers are sometimes available (for a fee), but you can’t always bank on their appeal. You might decide to take the plunge – but chances are you’ll soon be running away in horror at the sight of them.<\/p><p>Wet wipes and sanitizer will be your savior. OK, you won’t be sparkling clean, but you’ll feel a little fresher. Clean enough to cope and ready to take on the day.<\/p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "15d54bfe-1b48-43c0-9fad-0527a7874216",
        "16581501770ad7ecad-1"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Hand_sanitizer_and_wet_wipes.jpg",
